description:
This Free Photoshop & Lightroom course has more than 55 lessons to improve your post processing skills.

This free photography training course is for any passionate photographer looking to improve the quality of their images and efficacy of their workflow.

The course is divided into 4 chapters. Chapter 1 & 2 are all about Photoshop tutorials. Chapter 3 & 4 focus on Lightroom tutorials. There's even a bonus chapter full of non post processing photography tips!

Enjoy!
title: Photoshop & Lightroom for Photographers
